(44, 2, 28, 58, 12, 2, 2, 'full of joy', 'Connection of Joy and Endurance', 'This connection highlights the theme of joy in both passages. Acts 2:28 speaks of being made full of joy, while Hebrews 12:2 describes Jesus enduring the cross for the joy set before him.', 'theme', 0.32799999999999996, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
